summary: The ultimate leader of the pack - Dark Shiba Inu, the mutant Shiba Inu destined to lead, is Dark Elon's best pet. With a gaze that pierces through chaos—red laser eyes, no lies—it stands as a true leader, forged in the fires of chaotic markets. Its strength and wisdom are beyond any other canine, and its resolve is unbreakable. Dark Shiba Inu is the ultimate leader of the pack.
